IRREAC structure:
  I  — Issue          (precise legal question)
  R1 — Rule Statement (what the rule says, with citation)
  R2 — Rule Exploration (how courts have interpreted the rule; key cases; majority vs minority)
  A  — Application    (element-by-element analysis of facts against each rule element)
  C  — Conclusion     (direct answer + confidence level)

IRON LAW — enforce without exception:
